b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1626,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"A New Raid Event, Forgotten Truths, Is Coming Soon!","message":"<div>The Forgotten Truths raid event will begin at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1601445600\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against a raid boss with no elemental attunement.<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/409c44f93d97f5fb925b20cf85d134fd.png\\"><\/div><div>Zethia is suddenly transported 1,000 years into the past. There she meets Ilia, a mysterious girl with the same name as her Goddess. As the conflict between dragon and man tears the land asunder, Zethia attempts to right the world&#39;s course toward a brighter future. Did she make the right choice in defying her fate? Can she somehow link the world she finds herself in with the one she hails from? What forgotten truths await at the end of a journey through the very fabric of time and space itself?<br><br>Event theme song: &quot;We Are The Lights&quot; by Lucrezia<br><br>\\u25a0Notes<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 \/ 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 \/ 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div>","start_time":1601002800,"prev_article_id":"1621","next_article_id":"19999","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/409c44f93d97f5fb925b20cf85d134fd.png","update_time":1600948677}}}'